{"id": "art-2702c", "label": "Art. 2702c)", "title": "Art. 2702c)", "slug": "art-2702c", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_224341808\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1117\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_224341808\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 270<sup>2c)</sup></span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1098921569\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1116\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1098921569\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)Orice societate european&#259; înmatriculat&#259; în\nRomânia <span class=SpellE>î&#351;i</span> poate transfera sediul social\nîntr-un alt stat membru.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_740303134\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1115\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_740303134\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)Proiectul de transfer, vizat de registratorul de\nregistrul <span class=SpellE>comer&#355;ului</span>, se public&#259; în\nMonitorul Oficial al României, Partea a IV-a, pe cheltuiala <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>,\ncu cel <span class=SpellE>pu&#355;in</span> 30 de zile înaintea datei <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;edin&#355;ei</span> în care adunarea general&#259;\nextraordinar&#259; urmeaz&#259; a hot&#259;rî asupra transferului.</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_784751055\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1114\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_784751055\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)Hot&#259;rârea adun&#259;rii generale privind transferul\nsediului social al <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span> europene\nîntr-un alt stat membru se adopt&#259; în <span class=SpellE>condi&#355;iile</span>\nart. </span><span style='color:#1B1B1B'>115 alin. (2)</span><span\nstyle='color:black'>. În cazul în care <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;ionarii</span>\nreprezentând majoritatea capitalului social sunt <span class=SpellE>prezen&#355;i</span>\nsau <span class=SpellE>reprezentan&#355;i</span>, decizia poate fi\nadoptat&#259; cu majoritate simpl&#259;.</span></p>"}